| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7293 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9b772b32-f969-557d-b91c-fa0f8d5bb5d6"
